RES osdtriplet
SUR SA
PIK RDY S3 S1
RDY S1 45
SUR SA
PIK THI S4 S2 2.0
THI S2 4
SUR SA
! Next line is a deliberate error (CUY is not a valid surface parameter):
PIK CUY S3 S1
! Save/reload round-trip: both pickups must survive and stay LIVE
! (targets track new source values after reload).  Note THI pickups were
! historically dropped from saves entirely -- this guards that fix.
SAV pickuptest
RES pickuptest
RDY S1 40
THI S2 5
SUR SA
! Removal: after PIKD the targets must stop tracking the source.
U L
PIKD RD,3
PIKD TH,4
EOS
RDY S1 60
THI S2 7
SUR SA

! --- Glass pickup (PIK GLA, no scale/offset) ---
! S4 is air in osdtriplet; picking up S1's glass must fill it, survive a
! SAV/RES round-trip (glass pickups were historically dropped from saves --
! the writer's short 'PIK GLA Starget Ssource' form guards that fix), track a
! source glass change, and stop tracking after PIKD GLASS.
RES osdtriplet
PIK GLA S4 S1
SUR SA
SAV pickuptest
RES pickuptest
GLA S1 NF2_SCHOTT
SUR SA
U L
PIKD GLASS,4
EOS
GLA S1 NSK16_SCHOTT
SUR SA
